parameters:
\SE[29]I'm sorry for causing trouble.... \!\SE[60]Sigh... I
need to calm down....

\SE[5]However...\.This place is so mysterious....
\!\SE[54]It feels very comforting, \.yet at the same time,
it makes me a little anxious....

\SE[64]Ah...! I'm sorry for earlier...!! \SE[60]I was very
rude...

'Teacher: \SE[3]I'm not sure if I can be of any help....
\!\SE[0]May I listen to your story?'

'Teacher: \SE[2]I see...\.Indeed, I might be able to heal
you.'

'Teacher: \SE[9]I... might be able to. \.\SE[8]I can't say
for certain...!'

\SE[65]But it's difficult for me to get someone to look at
it.... \SE[24]I was told earlier that it's five years
later....

'Teacher: \SE[52]Um... If it was a case of mistaken
identity, I apologize...'

'Teacher: \SE[4]Are you... by any chance... \SE[3]Laura from
Zero Tsuki...?'

\SE[64]Um, yes... Embarrassingly enough... Somehow, I've
been called that... \SE[60]For me, it feels strange
though...

'Teacher: \SE[12]The patient I am currently seeing.... Their
condition is a bit critical. \SE[13]So, I would like to
treat them directly if possible....'

'Teacher: \SE[14]I alone... am lacking in power. \SE[13]So,
if I could borrow the power of Zero Tsuki Laura-san, and
cure that child's illness....'

'Teacher: \SE[14]I believe I can make time to check on
Lunaroa- san's condition. \SE[13]...What do you think?'
\SE[70]I'll do it!!! \!\SE[12]Please let me do it!!
